title: Gov't Mule - Mule On Easy Street [320k MP3]
description:
MULE ON EASY STREET

Released December 12th, 2006
Recorded Live @ Easy Street Records - 10.19.06
Available Only In Indie Record Stores (www.thinkindie.com)

TRACKLIST [320k MP3]

01. 	Hammer & Nails 		
02. 	Time To Confess 		
03. 	Million Miles From Yesterday 		
04. 	That's What Love Will Make You Do

On Tuesday December 12th, in independent record stores all over the country, a very special Live Mule EP titled "Mule on Easy Street" will become available. This is taken from the 10.19.06 performance at Easy Street Records in Seattle, WA. To find a store near you that will be carrying Mule on Easy Street head to www.thinkindie.com. This EP will ONLY be available in these INDEPENDENT record stores.
